  "claim_short": "Let E be any nonzero Banach space. For all Banach spaces X and Y, if (X, E \\hat{\\otimes}_\\epsilon Y) has the BPBp, then (X,Y) has the BPBp. Quantitatively, if (X, E \\hat{\\otimes}_\\epsilon Y) has BPBp modulus eta, then (X,Y) has BPBp modulus epsilon -> eta(epsilon/2).",
